+`0xc1ee` transfers all 155,200 USDC (77,600 × 2) back to `0xe022`. `0xe022`:
+- Sends 58,200 USDC profit to attacker EOA `0x7926`.
+- Repays the 97,000 USDC flash loan to Morpho.
