+## Financial Impact
+
+- **Protocol fees drained**: 23.12 BNB sent directly to the attacker EOA via `claimFees()`
+- **DXN reward tokens minted**: 9,676.9 DXN (bDXN) minted to the attacker EOA via `claimRewards()`
+- **Attacker net ETH profit**: 22.53 BNB (23.12 BNB received from `claimFees()` + 1.61 BNB residual, minus 2.2 BNB initial investment)
