+## Financial Impact
+
+| Address | Role | USDC Delta |
+|---------|------|-----------|
+| `0x61ce9b...` (Vault) | Victim — protocol collateral pool | **−165,647.735181 USDC** |
+| `0x374d78...` (aLinUSDC) | Aave fee | **+30.000000 USDC** (flash loan fee) |
