+| Attacker EOA (`0xdb0901a3`) | **+381.75 WBNB** profit |
+| Attacker Contract (`0xdf7ed22d`) | net ~0 WBNB (flash loan borrowed and repaid), net 0 MT |
+| MT/WBNB PancakeSwap Pair (`0x037e6eb2`) | **-381.75 WBNB**, **-7,735,517 MT** (reserves drained) |
