+              |       +-> DELEGATECALL FiatTokenV2_2.balanceOf()  [depth 6]
+              |   returns: 42606959179 (confirmed settlement)
+              |
+              +-> CALL PoolManager.take(                          [depth 4]
+                      ETH, attacker_EOA, 21197984596759249607)
