+### Forged Proof Structure
+
+From the first `withdraw()` calldata, the proof elements are:
+- **A** (pA): `[0x04c3a500..., 0x27cc7739...]` -- a fixed G1 point
+- **B** (pB): `[[0x0e629058..., 0x271c721e...], [0x1856fcac..., 0x2434fc73...]]` -- a fixed G2 point
